const dynamicFormNestItemValues = useState({
    bht_f: null,
    bht_psi: null,
    customer: null,
    date: null,
    event_occur: null,
    field_engineer_days: null,
    field_engineer_nights: null,
    frac_design: null,
    plug_seat_technique: null,
    plug_type: null,
    seismos_data_collection: null,
    stage: null,
})

const perforationIntervalInformationValues = useState({
    acid: null,
    bottom_perf: null,
    clusters_number: null,
    displacement_vol_bottom: null,
    displacement_vol_plug: null,
    displacement_vol_top: null,
    diverter_type: null,
    perf_daiameter: null,
    perf_gun_desc: null,
    plug_depth: null,
    pumped_diverter: null,
    spf: null,
    top_perf: null
})

const stageDataValues = useState({
    Acid_volume_gals: null,
    Flush_volume_bbls: null,
    Max_prop_Conc_ppa: null,
    Slurry_volume_bbls: null,
    Total_lbs: null,
    Total_clean_fluid_volume_bbls: null,
    Total_pad_volume_bbls: null,
    Total_sand_lbs: null,
    base_fluid_density: null,
    base_fluid_type: null,
    isip: null,
    last_bbls: null,
    last_description: null,
    last_ppg: null,
    max_conc_density: null,
    opening_well: null,
    second_bbls: null,
    second_description: null,
    second_ppg: null,
    stage_end_time: null,
    stage_start_time: null,
    third_bbls: null,
    third_description: null,
})

const propantFormValues = useState({
    proppantData: [
        {
            bulk_density: null,
            description: null,
            specific_gravity: null,
        }
    ]
})

const activeDataFormValues = useState({
    amplitude: null,
    frequency: null,
    number_of_pulses: null,
    offset: null,
    periods: null,
    post_end_time: null,
    post_start_time: null,
    pre_end_time: null,
    pre_start_time: null,
})

const notesFataFormValues = useState({
    other_notes: null,
    pre_notes: null,
    post_notes: null
})

const DefaultValues = {
    dynamicFormNestItemValues,
    perforationIntervalInformationValues,
    stageDataValues,
    propantFormValues,
    activeDataFormValues,
    notesFataFormValues,
}

export default FormInitialValues;
